comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T20:44:19.131Z",codex-root,Delivery step 6 is active on PR #60. Hosted checks and full paginated review inventory will be recorded before merge; any push will retrigger every requested review agent.
plan_mode: approved
plan_decisions[1]{ts,author,decision,rationale,evidence}:
  "2026-07-21T19:00:05.325Z",codex-root,Keep raw ws call as the forward-compatible full API surface and add typed helpers only for stable high-value discovery contracts.,Home Assistant WebSocket commands are dynamic and integration-dependent; typed affordances should improve agent UX without pretending the finite CLI can freeze every command.,Official WebSocket docs describe generic command envelopes and current target helper commands; existing ws call accepts arbitrary types.
plan_discoveries[1]{ts,author,text}:
  "2026-07-21T19:00:04.305Z",codex-root,Live settings validation fails before network I/O because Undici 8 rejects request-level throwOnError.
